WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.512
31 December 1986 A Temperament Of A Peaceful Personality
Mahalakshmi Puja
Sangli (India)

00:00:02.544 --> 00:00:12.880
Sahaja Yoga is spreading slowly in Sangli district.

00:00:12.880 --> 00:00:21.160
But the thing that spreads
slowly gets established firmly.

00:00:21.160 --> 00:00:24.620
And any live process
takes place slowly.

00:00:24.620 --> 00:00:31.040
Hence we should not expect that
it will suddenly grow on large scale.

00:00:31.040 --> 00:00:39.080
If we need to produce plastic flowers
then a machine is sufficient for that.

00:00:39.080 --> 00:00:45.200
But to create live
flowers, it takes time.

00:00:45.200 --> 00:00:51.000
It needs to be cultivated,
effort has to be taken.

00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:58.720
Many people still do not have
any idea about Sahaja Yoga.

00:00:58.720 --> 00:01:02.920
And those who know
have only misconceptions.

00:01:02.920 --> 00:01:11.840
We have many cults, sects which
are already active since long time.

00:01:11.840 --> 00:01:19.280
But we have not benefitted
from these cults and sects.

00:01:19.280 --> 00:01:23.640
“We have been going to Pandhari
(Pandharpur) for so many days,

00:01:23.640 --> 00:01:29.400
have been worshipping Tuljapur’s Bhavani
for so many days,

00:01:29.400 --> 00:01:35.748
have been visiting
Mahalakshmi temple at Kolhapur.

00:01:35.748 --> 00:01:39.200
We did everything
that is possible.

00:01:39.200 --> 00:01:41.864
Performed fasts and
religious ceremonies.

00:01:41.904 --> 00:01:46.388
Despite doing all this Mataji, we did
not get anything.”

00:01:46.412 --> 00:01:49.880
On the top of it, after
growing up your children

00:01:49.880 --> 00:01:53.080
will ask you; you have spent so much time,

00:01:53.080 --> 00:01:57.980
spent money, took efforts and
at end you did not gain anything.

00:01:57.980 --> 00:02:04.680
Means there is no God.

00:02:04.680 --> 00:02:10.840
If you wish to go to Sangli then
take a road leading to Sangli.

00:02:10.840 --> 00:02:16.600
If you take opposite route
then you will not reach Sangli.

00:02:16.600 --> 00:02:21.200
So after so many years,
you did not reach Sangli.

00:02:21.200 --> 00:02:24.868
It means that you were walking
on the wrong road,

00:02:24.892 --> 00:02:28.920
and are still wandering on the same road.

00:02:28.920 --> 00:02:33.000
We have not
yet found the way.

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:37.960
Everyone should have this
prudent thought

00:02:37.960 --> 00:02:41.404
Because we have not yet found the way,

00:02:41.416 --> 00:02:43.960
and we have not achieved anything.

00:02:43.960 --> 00:02:49.040
So we must think at least once, that something
has gone wrong,

00:02:49.040 --> 00:02:54.000
first understand Sahaja Yoga
and then explain it to people.

00:02:54.000 --> 00:02:58.560
While convincing people regarding this,

00:02:58.560 --> 00:03:02.280
one thing is very essential,

00:03:02.280 --> 00:03:05.160
means while speaking to
people with whom you connect,

00:03:05.160 --> 00:03:12.560
you should speak in their
language to convince them.

00:03:12.560 --> 00:03:16.420
If you use your language,
they will not follow.

00:03:16.420 --> 00:03:20.140
If we try to explain the chakras
directly, they will not understand.

00:03:20.140 --> 00:03:27.200
But if you tell, we have Kundalini power within us about which Dnyaneshwar has talked.

00:03:27.200 --> 00:03:31.348
You respectfully call him as
“Mauli”(mother)

00:03:31.372 --> 00:03:34.944
and take out religious processions and
dindis(parades) in his name

00:03:34.968 --> 00:03:37.300
But you must first read
what has been written by him.

00:03:37.300 --> 00:03:40.436
Now why has it been told to you that
you should not read the sixth chapter?

00:03:40.436 --> 00:03:42.280
Because if you read that,

00:03:42.292 --> 00:03:47.388
these people who
are leading you to the wrong path,

00:03:47.412 --> 00:03:51.280
people who are looting
you, will not benefit.

00:03:51.280 --> 00:03:52.816
Hence this has been written.

00:03:52.816 --> 00:03:56.028
If you tell people that whatever is written
in the sixth chapter is what we give you,

00:03:56.028 --> 00:03:58.920
then they will understand.

00:03:58.920 --> 00:04:02.584
Hence whatever first
we need to tell people,

00:04:02.608 --> 00:04:06.004
it should be explained in
their language, in their way.

00:04:06.004 --> 00:04:13.280
Secondly, as we have the guidance of
Namdeo, Tukram, Gora Kumbhar, Janabai,

00:04:13.280 --> 00:04:19.800
Muktabai, Dnyaneshwar and Ramdas

00:04:19.800 --> 00:04:25.800
after reading their books we should examine what all
is written in the poetic verses written in those books.

00:04:25.800 --> 00:04:29.648
Means what they have written about the
people engrossed in the misconceptions and

00:04:29.648 --> 00:04:32.880
who fast and perform
religious ceremonies.

00:04:32.880 --> 00:04:37.240
Dnyaneshwar himself has clearly written in
his book “Amrutanubhav”

00:04:37.240 --> 00:04:41.268
that after reading his book, one should simply
contemplate and think – what this is all about

00:04:41.292 --> 00:04:42.952
not merely continue reading.

00:04:42.952 --> 00:04:44.908
You will be surprised that

00:04:44.932 --> 00:04:47.148
he has stipulated in it more clearly

00:04:47.172 --> 00:04:50.348
than what I am emphasizing.

00:04:50.372 --> 00:04:59.268
Ramdas Swamy and Tukaram
have sweared at such people severely.

00:04:59.268 --> 00:05:02.960
Still these vagabonds
misguiding others.

00:05:02.960 --> 00:05:04.468
Somebody was talking to me the other day

00:05:04.480 --> 00:05:07.896
Mataji, you said not to apply bukka
(Black powder) on the forehead. Why is that?

00:05:07.896 --> 00:05:09.900
Where we apply bukka is
actually agnya chakra’s place.

00:05:09.900 --> 00:05:11.800
The sun is positioned
on agnya chakra.

00:05:11.800 --> 00:05:13.760
Do we apply black to the sun?

00:05:13.760 --> 00:05:16.052
But even from Sahaja
Yoga’s perspective we

00:05:16.052 --> 00:05:18.320
should ask them a
simple question, that the

00:05:18.320 --> 00:05:25.280
people who advise you to apply bukka, means
these priests sitting at Pandharpur

00:05:25.280 --> 00:05:29.520
They are aptly called Badwe (The
beaters), they actually beat people.

00:05:29.520 --> 00:05:32.576
These Badwes never wear bukka.

00:05:32.576 --> 00:05:35.916
No bhatji (priest) applies
black on his forehead.

00:05:35.916 --> 00:05:40.800
Then why should you apply black?

00:05:40.800 --> 00:05:43.696
If you ask them such pertinent questions,

00:05:43.696 --> 00:05:45.228
then it will dawn in their heads and if

00:05:45.228 --> 00:05:49.820
tomorrow his son gets waylaid
then you are responsible for that.

00:05:49.820 --> 00:05:58.640
Because by mechanically chanting
God’s name you have not achieved anything.

00:05:58.640 --> 00:06:00.940
You have not benefitted from it.

00:06:00.940 --> 00:06:03.804
This has to be
clearly told to them.

00:06:03.804 --> 00:06:08.200
Only after telling them
clearly, they will realize.

00:06:08.200 --> 00:06:11.424
If even one out of hundred comes to his
senses, if even one person comes to his

00:06:11.424 --> 00:06:16.920
senses then we must think
that a lot has been gained.

00:06:16.920 --> 00:06:23.204
But if anyone becomes stubborn, anyone
becomes obstinate

00:06:23.228 --> 00:06:25.608
then there is no need to
tell him about Sahaja Yoga.

00:06:25.608 --> 00:06:28.216
Christ has clearly mentioned that

00:06:28.240 --> 00:06:31.760
one should not pour pearls
in front of pigs.

00:06:31.760 --> 00:06:33.800
They do not understand anything

00:06:33.800 --> 00:06:35.900
then why to pour pearls in front of them?

00:06:35.900 --> 00:06:36.940
These are pearls.

00:06:36.940 --> 00:06:38.316
These are pearls from life.

00:06:38.316 --> 00:06:39.620
You will not understand.

00:06:39.620 --> 00:06:41.000
It should be in your fate.

00:06:41.000 --> 00:06:42.276
It is not in your luck.

00:06:42.276 --> 00:06:43.900
It seems to have dozed off.

00:06:43.900 --> 00:06:46.560
Or it is destroyed somewhere.

00:06:46.560 --> 00:06:48.920
So this needs fortune/luck.

00:06:48.920 --> 00:06:52.640
In addition, it needs
people who are full of valor.

00:06:52.640 --> 00:06:54.800
In the beginning there
are lots of on lookers.

00:06:54.800 --> 00:06:57.080
I see, lots of onlookers
in the program.

00:06:57.080 --> 00:07:00.676
Hence in the program on the
first day, there is a lot of rush.

00:07:00.676 --> 00:07:02.296
Overflowing crowd.

00:07:02.296 --> 00:07:05.280
On the second day there
will be half the number.

00:07:05.280 --> 00:07:07.072
The reason is that
The onlookers have dropped out.

00:07:07.072 --> 00:07:09.160
Good riddance.
Otherwise it is a headache.

00:07:09.160 --> 00:07:12.380
Now if there are many onlookers,
they will not become Sahaja Yogis.

00:07:12.380 --> 00:07:14.092
But will keep on watching.

00:07:14.092 --> 00:07:17.920
When the onlookers get dropped
then half the crowd remains.

00:07:17.920 --> 00:07:24.920
In that half, only the brave and valiant …

00:07:24.920 --> 00:07:30.588
it’s not for any Tom Dick and Harry

00:07:30.612 --> 00:07:35.800
very clearly mentioned  it's not
the work of any lay person.

00:07:35.800 --> 00:07:38.976
Means one should
have the caliber for this.

00:07:38.976 --> 00:07:42.280
In Marathi language, very apt
descriptions are available for everything.

00:07:42.280 --> 00:07:47.020
And For Sahaja Yoga, it is a very
elegant language and it is so useful.

00:07:47.020 --> 00:07:49.064
If you are proficient in Marathi

00:07:49.088 --> 00:07:50.696
and if you need to speak with
Marathi people

00:07:50.720 --> 00:07:53.120
then you must be able to
convince them of Sahaja Yoga.

00:07:53.120 --> 00:07:56.080
You should be able to
convince them logically.

00:07:56.080 --> 00:07:58.896
It needs people with caliber.

00:07:58.896 --> 00:08:05.720
You don’t have the
caliber so good bye. Go.

00:08:05.720 --> 00:08:09.228
The word is “jativant” (true born)

00:08:09.252 --> 00:08:15.176
and It is said about the Devi (Goddess) “ya devi sarvabhuteshu jatirupen sansthita”
(The deity (devi) who is the main reason for creation of all the living beings)

00:08:15.176 --> 00:08:17.036
You are created with a distinct capability.

00:08:17.060 --> 00:08:20.760
If you do not have the natural ability to
receive it, how can I bestow it upon you?

00:08:20.760 --> 00:08:25.440
Jaat does not mean
Bramhan or shudra.

00:08:25.440 --> 00:08:33.180
Jaat means our inner tendency which
is called as aptitude.

00:08:33.180 --> 00:08:34.640
It is a tendency.

00:08:34.640 --> 00:08:36.800
What is that aptitude?

00:08:36.800 --> 00:08:42.040
A person’s Jaat (class) is
dependent on his aptitude.

00:08:42.040 --> 00:08:47.200
And everything is written
in Devi’s description.

00:08:47.200 --> 00:08:48.528
Complete description is there.

00:08:48.528 --> 00:08:51.368
You will find each and every
description given exactly in Sahaja Yoga.

00:08:51.368 --> 00:08:55.800
“Shobhana sulabha gati,
Shobhana sulabha gati, sulabha gati.”

00:08:55.800 --> 00:08:59.680
It has a pace that is easy.

00:08:59.680 --> 00:09:03.440
Means that which gets
done easily and is elegant.

00:09:03.440 --> 00:09:06.116
In this, you need not shout or yell,

00:09:06.140 --> 00:09:09.708
don’t have to behave in a tipsy
manner in a dindi (procession),

00:09:09.732 --> 00:09:11.528
don’t have to behave like crazy.

00:09:11.528 --> 00:09:12.436
Absolutely nothing.

00:09:12.436 --> 00:09:14.220
“Shobhana sulabha gati”.

00:09:14.220 --> 00:09:16.800
Many people are
just being volatile.

00:09:16.800 --> 00:09:20.516
You can see that some people’s meditation
is very odd

00:09:20.540 --> 00:09:24.600
that one feels like running away

00:09:24.600 --> 00:09:28.464
they shout, scream,
tear their clothes

00:09:28.488 --> 00:09:30.920
such is their way of mediation.

00:09:30.920 --> 00:09:33.988
“Shobhana sulabha gati”
Is the description for Devi.

00:09:33.988 --> 00:09:36.616
She gives you
“Shobhana sulabha gati”.

00:09:36.616 --> 00:09:39.856
If this is the description of Devi,
and if it happens accordingly,

00:09:39.856 --> 00:09:43.680
then why do you
drag your feet to go there?

00:09:43.680 --> 00:09:48.200
Why to take so much trouble?

00:09:48.200 --> 00:09:53.464
But it does not mean that those who were
pundarikasksha (lotuseyed),

00:09:53.488 --> 00:09:58.108
the saints that have been,

00:09:58.132 --> 00:10:04.080
I am not denying them or
talking derogatory about them.

00:10:04.080 --> 00:10:07.032
Or for that matter even
Shrikrishna is there.

00:10:07.032 --> 00:10:12.920
And his place is at
Pandharpur, no doubt about it.

00:10:12.920 --> 00:10:14.428
Pandhari is real.

00:10:14.428 --> 00:10:18.508
But the charlatans sitting there,
they are present at each holy place.

00:10:18.508 --> 00:10:24.000
But that does not mean that Pandhari
is false and these people are true.

00:10:24.000 --> 00:10:27.616
If we fix a stone in gold, the stone does
not turn into diamond

00:10:27.640 --> 00:10:33.680
and we fix stone in gold, the
gold does not turn into brass.

00:10:33.680 --> 00:10:38.904
Hence even if both the things are true,

00:10:38.928 --> 00:10:42.956
that one is based on truth
and the other on falsity,

00:10:42.980 --> 00:10:46.324
and even if they are paired forcibly,

00:10:46.348 --> 00:10:48.948
still, using the competence to differentiate
between water and milk, we must show them that

00:10:48.972 --> 00:10:53.148
these two things are different.

00:10:53.172 --> 00:10:58.540
After showing this they will
understand,” Oh my God. What is this?"

00:10:58.540 --> 00:11:00.800
They are speaking
like saint Tukaram.

00:11:00.800 --> 00:11:05.240
Their talk is very
enlightening”.

00:11:05.240 --> 00:11:09.348
Similarly to have saptah (sermons for
entire week), this and that

00:11:09.372 --> 00:11:13.120
these things are
of a social nature here.

00:11:13.120 --> 00:11:15.500
To arrange saptah
has a social aspect.

00:11:15.500 --> 00:11:20.960
First the saptah is done, then
meals, then sitting without purpose.

00:11:20.960 --> 00:11:25.452
On this, Kabir has said- “Padhi padhi pandit murakh bhaye” (Just reading without understanding makes a learned person an idiot).

00:11:25.452 --> 00:11:28.480
They just keep on reading.

00:11:28.480 --> 00:11:32.696
“kahe nanak bin aapachi ne, mita na bhram
ki kayi”,

00:11:32.720 --> 00:11:38.400
keep on chanting this for one’s amusement and learn it by heart as well. (Nanak says – to
know yourself you need to remove the shroud of illusion of worldly love and attractions )

00:11:38.400 --> 00:11:40.560
Then there is one parrot.

00:11:40.560 --> 00:11:45.396
His master trained him to say
‘raghupati raghav rajaram’

00:11:45.420 --> 00:11:46.156
He learnt.

00:11:46.156 --> 00:11:49.260
After he started parroting, listening to
him, another parrot started saying the same thing.

00:11:49.260 --> 00:11:52.880
Means the first parrot
is the guru of the second one.

00:11:52.880 --> 00:11:58.820
The number of gurus thus increased
creating a lineage of jabberers.

00:11:58.820 --> 00:12:00.448
Tell them that

00:12:00.448 --> 00:12:04.760
if you wish to have the truth, you need to
come out of this jabbering.

00:12:04.760 --> 00:12:07.716
Thus Marathi has so much of humor also

00:12:07.740 --> 00:12:15.440
hence I feel this language has been created
for Sahaja Yoga only.

00:12:15.440 --> 00:12:19.828
Every word has so much subtlety,

00:12:19.852 --> 00:12:26.400
so you can be confident and
use this language fully.

00:12:26.400 --> 00:12:30.160
As there is a saying here – ‘ati shahane tyache bail rikame’
(people who show over intelligence are usually losers).

00:12:30.160 --> 00:12:32.652
To begin with they are pseudo wise,
on the top of it, they are over smart.

00:12:32.652 --> 00:12:35.780
You cannot explain
this in any language.

00:12:35.800 --> 00:12:40.476
The next level of being pseudo wise
is being an unbridled brash individual.

00:12:40.476 --> 00:12:44.040
Such individuals incur losses.

00:12:44.040 --> 00:12:46.144
This cannot be explained
in any other language.

00:12:46.144 --> 00:12:52.280
This can be expressed
only in our Marathi Language.

00:12:52.280 --> 00:12:56.920
That’s why one should utilize
this language completely.

00:12:56.920 --> 00:12:59.420
Even if you are absorbed in the
contemplation of Bramha (The Absolute)

00:12:59.444 --> 00:13:01.128
and you have achieved Bramha,

00:13:01.152 --> 00:13:02.892
you are practicing it with dedication

00:13:02.916 --> 00:13:04.472
and it is flowing through you,

00:13:04.496 --> 00:13:08.912
and similarly with pure consciousness flowing,
if everybody wishes to understand the Bramha,

00:13:08.936 --> 00:13:12.428
still to become a guru

00:13:12.452 --> 00:13:19.080
one should know whatever is the
traditional knowledge in this world.

00:13:19.080 --> 00:13:21.680
And one should be thoroughly
conversant with Ved Shastra.

00:13:21.680 --> 00:13:23.920
This does not mean
having read Vedas.

00:13:23.920 --> 00:13:32.000
But one should have the knowledge, after examining
the summary of what other Sadhus and saints have said.

00:13:32.000 --> 00:13:39.508
There is no need to do some special
reading or do some special deed.

00:13:39.508 --> 00:13:43.500
Only need to cultivate a little
hobby of reading books daily.

00:13:43.500 --> 00:13:45.128
Everyone will understand
after doing the reading.

00:13:45.128 --> 00:13:49.960
Because once you become a Sahaja Yogi,
whatever he may be, he understands everything.

00:13:49.960 --> 00:13:57.480
Thus in this way, one can
position the second point.

00:13:57.480 --> 00:14:04.120
The third point is that people who
are over smart, they will preach you.

00:14:04.120 --> 00:14:06.508
When they start saying ‘Tuka mhane aise’
(Saint Tukaram Says thus),

00:14:06.532 --> 00:14:09.920
you ask them ‘Tuka Mahne Kaise’ (what does
Tukaram say?), this should have a response.

00:14:09.920 --> 00:14:14.788
And another thing is when they say ‘Tuka
mhane aise’, one should know the context here.

00:14:14.812 --> 00:14:16.024
They just keep on blabbering something.

00:14:16.024 --> 00:14:17.204
All the sayings of
Tukaram are over.

00:14:17.204 --> 00:14:19.104
Now they will append something of their own
in Tuka’s name like

00:14:19.128 --> 00:14:23.080
‘Tuka says that apply bukka(black powder applied on agya)’. Excellent, is that so?

00:14:23.080 --> 00:14:25.380
Was there bukka (black
powder) available in those days?

00:14:25.380 --> 00:14:28.228
They just attribute such things to Tukaram.
This is the third practice in their name.

00:14:28.252 --> 00:14:32.924
That you must apply bukka

00:14:32.948 --> 00:14:38.960
though the word bukka is not
mentioned in any of their verses.

00:14:38.960 --> 00:14:45.136
Even if the word, Varkari (person on pilgrimage) is not
mentioned, they will say ‘Tuka says become a Varkari’.

00:14:45.136 --> 00:14:50.080
This way, force people in
his name and speak lies.

00:14:50.080 --> 00:14:52.256
Tomorrow they will
say, ‘Mataji says….

00:14:52.256 --> 00:14:55.120
Not only my name,
one could use any name.

00:14:55.120 --> 00:15:00.036
If we want to use, then we can use anybody’s
name such as Mataji says apply bukka.

00:15:00.036 --> 00:15:06.500
Now recently someone attributed to me that
‘Mataji says keep a fast, should not eat’.

00:15:06.500 --> 00:15:10.120
This is great.

00:15:10.120 --> 00:15:20.468
Thus different types of repeated aggressive
onslaughts may come on you;

00:15:20.492 --> 00:15:23.496
one should be
able to face those.

00:15:23.496 --> 00:15:27.120
This fight is for a short time.

00:15:27.120 --> 00:15:31.440
Once this fight gets over,
these people will be trounced.

00:15:31.440 --> 00:15:33.080
Totally vanquished.

00:15:33.080 --> 00:15:35.456
This is not a fight with Aurangjeb(King from India),

00:15:35.480 --> 00:15:37.080
It is fight against ignorance.

00:15:37.080 --> 00:15:39.988
The moment the light of knowledge enters it,

00:15:40.012 --> 00:15:41.720
these people will get vanquished.

00:15:41.720 --> 00:15:44.800
Because it is in their interest.

00:15:44.800 --> 00:15:48.600
We are telling you
this in your interest.

00:15:48.600 --> 00:15:51.920
You should tell them that we are
telling you things that will benefit you.

00:15:51.920 --> 00:15:57.120
This will enlighten their minds
and everything will be alright.

00:15:57.120 --> 00:16:02.368
My today’s speech should be taped and then
sent after transcribing it properly

00:16:02.392 --> 00:16:06.720
because it will be useful for everybody.

00:16:17.840 --> 00:16:23.840
I have been telling them, how they
have to face the other people around.

00:16:23.840 --> 00:16:27.748
You have the same problems a little more
sophisticated,

00:16:27.772 --> 00:16:30.476
and here the problems
are not so sophisticated

00:16:30.500 --> 00:16:33.640
because we don’t have organized religions.

00:16:33.640 --> 00:16:36.400
Thank God for that also,

00:16:36.400 --> 00:16:39.988
but because you have organized religions

00:16:40.012 --> 00:16:43.868
you have to face them in an organized way.

00:16:43.868 --> 00:16:48.856
For example, now here we have a custom that

00:16:48.880 --> 00:16:51.760
all the people who have to go to Vitthal,

00:16:51.760 --> 00:16:58.668
to see Vitthala in Pandharpur have to wear
a black spot,

00:16:58.692 --> 00:17:01.520
just the opposite of what it should be

00:17:01.520 --> 00:17:06.320
but the people who are in
charge, the priests, never wear black.

00:17:06.320 --> 00:17:10.800
You are misguided.

00:17:10.800 --> 00:17:17.348
But the religions across the oceans have

00:17:17.372 --> 00:17:23.400
become so organized, and are so solid,
absolutely solidified.

00:17:23.400 --> 00:17:27.108
That’s gone into their brain so much, that
if they have to give,

00:17:27.132 --> 00:17:34.480
give up those ideas
which are absolutely gross.

00:17:34.480 --> 00:17:36.640
they think that that they
will have to give up God.

00:17:36.640 --> 00:17:38.600
They are so much identified.

00:17:38.600 --> 00:17:40.700
Church is identified with God.

00:17:40.700 --> 00:17:49.920
Church has become God
and God has become Church.

00:17:49.920 --> 00:18:01.360
Actually in Sanskrit language church,
‘churchit’ means, which is worshipped, worship.

00:18:01.360 --> 00:18:07.640
But here at least in this country, thank
God we don’t have such an organized religion

00:18:07.640 --> 00:18:12.040
I mean an ordinary person can go
and challenge Shankaracharya,

00:18:12.040 --> 00:18:14.900
and can tell him off.

00:18:14.900 --> 00:18:17.720
But not in that country.

00:18:17.720 --> 00:18:20.416
You will have to just shoot
him down or something like that.

00:18:20.416 --> 00:18:21.928
There is no other way out.

00:18:21.928 --> 00:18:25.120
You cannot go and talk to
them and argue with them.

00:18:25.120 --> 00:18:28.584
So best thing would be to approach such
people

00:18:28.608 --> 00:18:35.880
who have been, eh, opposing those things

00:18:35.880 --> 00:18:38.228
but they may be the other kind,

00:18:38.252 --> 00:18:44.636
another blind who are in some ways, or
some things as who are denouncing God.

00:18:44.636 --> 00:18:48.760
Because if they denounce the
Church they also denounce God.

00:18:48.760 --> 00:18:52.108
So you should find out such people
who are

00:18:52.132 --> 00:18:56.428
understanding that there is God
but there is no church.

00:18:56.428 --> 00:19:00.400
I think there is a big
population of that kind.

00:19:00.400 --> 00:19:04.680
While talking to them you
have to know Bible very well.

00:19:04.680 --> 00:19:07.640
If you have to be a real Guru
you must know Bible

00:19:07.640 --> 00:19:09.756
because you cannot talk
to them without it.

00:19:09.756 --> 00:19:16.160
And also other religions in which there
is a complete explanation of Sahaja Yoga.

00:19:16.160 --> 00:19:20.632
If you know Bible how far it is
closer to Sahaja Yoga you can talk to them.

00:19:20.632 --> 00:19:23.620
If you know about Christ very
well then you can talk to them.

00:19:23.620 --> 00:19:26.408
So you can say chapter
this and this and this.

00:19:26.408 --> 00:19:28.600
You should say chapter
this and this, this and this.

00:19:28.600 --> 00:19:33.280
As soon as they say chapter this one
and this one, your open argument shows.

00:19:33.280 --> 00:19:37.428
So you must neutralize their arguments by

00:19:37.452 --> 00:19:40.880
your own knowledge which is enlightened.

00:19:40.880 --> 00:19:44.504
The best one you can say is that,

00:19:44.528 --> 00:19:51.028
that now since Christ departed from
this Earth you have been following them

00:19:51.052 --> 00:19:56.960
and you are aware what have you gained?
Nothing.

00:19:56.960 --> 00:20:01.268
Now in the Bible it is described that He
is going to send a counsellor,

00:20:01.268 --> 00:20:05.760
a comforter and a redeemer, what about that?

00:20:05.760 --> 00:20:09.400
Why don’t you seek for that?

00:20:09.400 --> 00:20:15.800
The arguments should not be
bombastic or aggressive but peaceful.

00:20:15.800 --> 00:20:19.668
In between, you must keep quiet for a
while, listen to the person

00:20:19.692 --> 00:20:23.800
and then tell them, I
am sure it will work out.

00:20:23.800 --> 00:20:28.068
As you know some of you must have
asked me questions also

00:20:28.092 --> 00:20:30.920
and I must have answered
them very well.

00:20:30.920 --> 00:20:36.720
But peacefully, joyfully
because they can not disturb you.

00:20:36.720 --> 00:20:41.840
You have to disturb them and their
fossilized ideas,

00:20:41.840 --> 00:20:46.480
which are to be defroze

00:20:46.480 --> 00:20:51.040
and for that you have
to have a temperament,

00:20:51.040 --> 00:20:56.640
a temperament of a peaceful personality.

00:20:56.640 --> 00:21:01.240
I have told in general to you but
quite intensely to these people.

00:21:01.240 --> 00:21:04.748
I told here to make a proper tape out of
that

00:21:04.760 --> 00:21:12.400
and I should translate it and put it in the
book that I am writing for the Sahaja Yogis.

00:21:12.400 --> 00:21:18.000
I am supposed to be writing.

00:21:18.000 --> 00:21:21.288
So now we are looking forward

00:21:21.312 --> 00:21:25.060
to going to Ganapatipule after this puja.

00:21:25.060 --> 00:21:30.668
I would request you to go with devotion

00:21:30.680 --> 00:21:36.880
and with complete surrendering
that you have to achieve something.

00:21:36.880 --> 00:21:39.480
Forget the past,
forget the past.

00:21:39.480 --> 00:21:41.240
You have to forget the past.

00:21:41.240 --> 00:21:46.760
It is very important that you
forget the past and then go there.

00:21:46.760 --> 00:21:49.204
Whatever has happened, has happened
in your life,

00:21:49.228 --> 00:21:52.568
is nothing important,
nothing can curb you down.

00:21:52.568 --> 00:21:57.788
You are like a new budding flower and
you have every right to be a fruit

00:21:57.812 --> 00:22:09.920
and no energy which is negative or so called
over positive can subdue or destroy you.

00:22:09.920 --> 00:22:14.800
Go with that idea, that
I am the Spirit

00:22:14.800 --> 00:22:17.508
and I have nothing to fear.

00:22:17.508 --> 00:22:20.624
May God bless you all!
